column2:
"<%me>.
The present day, I see thou art lone."
"Sayeth nay more... I has't hath heard everything from yond fellow, Xiao. I understandeth the situation at handeth."
"Neither thyself nor Matoi shouldst be blamed for this, I would has't done the same. Rather, thee shouldst be hailed as heroes for this."
"Matoi pushed everything from herself, to protect those she cared about."
"The lady hath decided what the lady did want to protect, and very much didst that."
"Yond's very much wonderful... I am honored to be her friend."
"And yet... I cannot findeth myself able to praise what she didst."
"How can the lady has't \"protected\" us at which hour, she hasn't protected us from sorrow."
"Tis a sorrowful tale, to depart from thine own world. Recall yonder."
"Due to mine own agelessness, I has't recall countless goodbyes throughout generations. So believeth in mine own words of wisdom at which hour I hath said all of yond. Kaka!"
